  "3334430": {
    "name": "The Fool's Apprentice",
    "steam_appid": 3334430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/e5a504df74c95a4c8ea9d27842887409.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/c746e22e6e95f67899306f7c7c255fb2.poster.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/c746e22e6e95f67899306f7c7c255fb2.webm?t=1758210403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>傻瓜学徒》是一款模拟魔法学校的游戏，玩家将扮演来自同名名门望族的法师 神术师塔恩。作为一名出色的魔法师，你要指导你的徒弟们学习一些知识......确保他们不会超出正确课程的范围。让他们悬浮起来 把他们扔来扔去 控制他们的思想或抹去他们的记忆 甚至把他们扔进通往其他世界的传送门里  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好的学徒肯定能活下来。至于坏的，教授又能做什么呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/970708ef2212edcdcc8f7db1fdb116bd.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/40bac720c632f3a58c1ea782ff97ff89.poster.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/40bac720c632f3a58c1ea782ff97ff89.webm?t=1758210403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>通过以下工具，在您的音乐学院掌舵下规划魔法的未来：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让新学徒接受你的指导，管理他们的技能，用法术指导他们学习，引导他们远离意外死亡！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行研究，用它来升级魔法工作站或解锁新的科学！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >应对困境，您为奥术学院做出的选择将决定人类在这个魔法与科学新时代的未来！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">绑架公民进行实验。</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为阳光下的运河城市戈尔里昂带来神奇的科学进步，赢得公众的爱戴！但要小心，对公众隐瞒每一点魔法可能会导致他们暴动！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/03024d4ef39a59050b376f710c24b455.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/23e615099c218c421760b7f1fcb8d1b5.poster.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/23e615099c218c421760b7f1fcb8d1b5.webm?t=1758210403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>新时代来临！人们发现了奥术科学，以及与之相关的魔法机械研究领域，并建造出了法术精深、设计巧妙的工程奇迹......是时候培养下一代学徒了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位巫师将教导他们... 你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定战略并建造理想的音乐学院，选择魔法研究的重点领域，不同风险、效果和难度的奥术工作站，以及具有长生力量的装饰品！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理每个学徒并为他们施法，引导他们远离 “野心 ”和 “艺术激情 ”等愚蠢的东西，学习社会最认可的魔法......或者与奥术学院本身对抗，在人群中传播魔法！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款魔法师学院模拟器中，装饰和定制你自己的奥术学院！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款魔法师学院模拟器中，您可以装饰和定制自己的奥术学院！在叙事驱动下，参与戈尔里昂魔法城市的需求起伏。前一天，音乐学院可能会要求增加元素大炮的产量；而第二天，公爵可能会要求您向远房表亲传授魔法！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽量不要因为奥术渎职罪入狱。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/69e0d2e19b075b4f61441987e0861bf3.poster.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/69e0d2e19b075b4f61441987e0861bf3.webm?t=1758210403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/69e0d2e19b075b4f61441987e0861bf3.mp4?t=1758210403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/cc1a88c0842f3c3ce37a3625648e39f2.avif?t=1758210403\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>The Fool's Apprentice</i>》再次回归《<i>The Planar Danse</i>》，这是《<i>Apollyon</i>》、《<i>Skulltide</i>》和《<i>Spirit's Almanac</i>》的连接宇宙，前几款游戏和小说都是在同一个世界中设定的。这款游戏可无限重玩，但所有解锁都可在约 8 小时的游戏时间内完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造魔法的未来，就在今天！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras/c6d46ea34c104f297434b8a0e792b6e5.avif?t=1758210403\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334430/extras_big/c6d46ea34c104f297434b8a0e792b6e5.avif?t=1758210403 width=800 height=413 /></span></p>",
